Evolution Markets to Use Trayport System for European Power

-- B y   L a r s   P a u l s s o n
-- 
2011-02-14T16:41:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-14/evolution-markets-to-use-trayport-system-for-european-power.html
Evolution Markets LLC, a broker that
started to offer European power last week, agreed to use a
trading system designed by  GFI Group Inc .’s Trayport Ltd. for
its electricity market.  The companies didn’t disclose financial details of the
accord in the e-mailed announcement today. GFI, the New York-
based inter-dealer broker of derivatives and securities, bought
Trayport in February 2008.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lars Paulsson in London at 
 lpaulsson@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stephen Voss at   sev@bloomberg.net  